Run ADE shipping phases (Commit & PR + Retrospective) for: $ARGUMENTS

1. Phase 9 — Commit & PR:
   - Stage relevant files (not .env, credentials, or unrelated changes)
   - Commit with conventional message (imperative mood, max 72 chars)
   - Push to feature branch
   - Open PR with summary, acceptance criteria, test plan

2. ◆ MERGE GATE — Present PR to user for review and merge decision

3. Phase 10 — Retrospective:
   - Record cycle time per phase, iteration counts
   - What worked, what didn't
   - Save to `.ade/tasks/<task-id>/retro.json`
   - Clean up worktree after merge
